title: Easter Rabbit Holiday Screensaver
description:
ABOUT THIS SCREENSAVER:

Take part in the Easter holiday with this beautiful screensaver.
Would you like your computer to have an animated and beautiful
screensaver? Easter, the Sunday of the Resurrection, or
Resurrection Day, is the most important religious feast for the
Christians. It celebrates the resurrection of Jesus, which his
followers believe occurred on the third day after his death by
crucifixion. Decorated eggs is symbols of Easter, and both eggs
and rabbits are age-old fertility symbols.
